data.description: This charming single story home is the perfect find for those seeking a comfortable and convenient living space. Inside you'll immediately notice the beautiful wood-like laminate flooring that brings the home an added touch of elegance along with the ample amount of natural light brought in from all of the windows throughout. The open floor plan creates a seamless flow between the Livingroom & dining area making it ideal for entertaining guest. The kitchen brings in a lot of natural light and includes all white appliances and a spacious pantry. The three bedrooms are well-sized & the primary offers ample closet space as well as a large en-suite bathroom w/dual vanities. Step outside to the private backyard with a covered patio that allows year around enjoyment and offers a serene space to unwind. Located in a desirable neighborhood this house offers convenience & accessibility to MANY nearby amenities such as schools, parks, shopping & more. Also includes SOLAR!
